kelas magang.

117
00:10:26,775 --> 00:10:28,535
Kamu tidak boleh melupakan
cita-cita awalmu."

118
00:10:30,936 --> 00:10:32,417
Aku sudah bertanya pada diriku sendiri.

119
00:10:32,857 --> 00:10:33,657
Saya berkata,

120
00:10:33,936 --> 00:10:34,736
"Zhao Li Quan,

121
00:10:35,176 --> 00:10:36,829
